edu.ncsu.csc216.travel.model.vacation

Class Tour

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.travel.model.vacation.Tour
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Tour>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EducationalTrip, LandTour, RiverCruise

    public abstract class Tour
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Tour>
    An abstract class representing a Wolf Travel tour. Every tour maintains a list of reservations for that tour. Has getters for each of its name, start date, duration, capacity, whether or not capacity is fixed, base price, and list of reservations fields. fields. Also has methods to compare tours, set the capacity, get the number of client reservations, get the number of spaces left for the tour, fix the capacity of the tour, get the end date of the tour, get a specific reservation, get a summary of the tour information, create reservations, add reservations, and cancel reservations.
    Author:
    Selena Chen, Alex Snezhko
